name: “Unawareness” by potentialight.art
description: @potentialight Hicetnunc Exclusive ✦ 2020 px x 2020 px 33/33 edition.   ⦿ “Unawareness” is about the blindspots and the darkness that goes unnoticed. That accumulates in the vast emptiness. The unawareness that can be transmuted into awareness by the small act of acknowledging that it exists. The smallest act of deciding to look within and shed light onto it. In the cave you fear to enter lies the treasure you seek.
